190
00:11:01,980 --> 00:11:02,920
So for example,

191
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:07,100
if I took the highest drinking person,
which was only eight drinks per week.

192
00:11:07,100 --> 00:11:08,470
And again, I made them an alcoholic.

193
00:11:08,470 --> 00:11:13,270
I said that that value, the highest
