194
00:11:13,270 --> 00:11:15,080
How does that effect the median?

195
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,710
Well, it doesn't effect the median, right,

196
00:11:16,710 --> 00:11:22,730
because 50% of people are still below two
and 50% of people are still above two.

197
00:11:22,730 --> 00:11:26,250
It doesn't matter that the highest person
is, it doesn't matter whether they're at

198
00:11:26,250 --> 00:11:30,550
eight or whether they're at 40, that
doesn't effect where the median lies.

199
00:11:30,550 --> 00:11:33,532
So the median is not effected by extreme
